  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Embark on a Pixelated Journey of Epic Proportions</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lando Me? A Hero? plunges you into a vibrant, pixelated world where your journey begins when an angel transports you to a realm on the brink of destruction. With diverse worlds to explore and an array of unique powers to wield, every playthrough offers fresh challenges and exhilarating gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252090/extras/f54d396b5a54738f0cf9cdea943247da.avif?t=1731603931\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252090/extras_big/f54d396b5a54738f0cf9cdea943247da.avif?t=1731603931 width=800 height=402 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unleash Your Power</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into fast-paced combat as you hack, slash, and strategize through handcrafted levels. Combine powers in creative ways to overcome relentless enemies and adapt to the ever-changing challenges ahead. Choose your path and make crucial decisions that will shape your adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252090/extras/6635edec80d04c60126dbfe5a4ff4e72.avif?t=1731603931\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252090/extras_big/6635edec80d04c60126dbfe5a4ff4e72.avif?t=1731603931 width=800 height=444 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Your Fate Awaits Will You Rise or Fall?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you prevail as the hero this world needs, or will you falter like those before you?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252090/extras/4b37c4bd6ed384e86a7214916628dae3.avif?t=1731603931\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252090/extras_big/4b37c4bd6ed384e86a7214916628dae3.avif?t=1731603931 width=800 height=444 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Embark on a Pixelated Journey of Epic Proportions</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lando Me? A Hero? plunges you into a vibrant, pixelated world where your journey begins when an angel transports you to a realm on the brink of destruction. With diverse worlds to explore and an array of unique powers to wield, every playthrough offers fresh challenges and exhilarating gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252090/extras/f54d396b5a54738f0cf9cdea943247da.avif?t=1731603931\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252090/extras_big/f54d396b5a54738f0cf9cdea943247da.avif?t=1731603931 width=800 height=402 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unleash Your Power</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into fast-paced combat as you hack, slash, and strategize through handcrafted levels. Combine powers in creative ways to overcome relentless enemies and adapt to the ever-changing challenges ahead. Choose your path and make crucial decisions that will shape your adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252090/extras/6635edec80d04c60126dbfe5a4ff4e72.avif?t=1731603931\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252090/extras_big/6635edec80d04c60126dbfe5a4ff4e72.avif?t=1731603931 width=800 height=444 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Your Fate Awaits Will You Rise or Fall?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you prevail as the hero this world needs, or will you falter like those before you?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252090/extras/4b37c4bd6ed384e86a7214916628dae3.avif?t=1731603